This API allows you to manage your Clusters for Apache Kafka®.

USAGE:
  scw kafka <command>

AVAILABLE COMMANDS:
  cluster     Cluster management commands
  endpoint    Endpoints management commands
  node-type   Node types management commands
  users       Kafka users management commands
  version     Kafka version management commands

FLAGS:
  -h, --help                help for kafka
      --list-sub-commands   List all subcommands

GLOBAL FLAGS:
  -B, --beta             Enable beta mode
  -c, --config string    The path to the config file
  -D, --debug            Enable debug mode
  -o, --output string    Output format: json or human, see 'scw help output' for more info (default "human")
  -p, --profile string   The config profile to use

Use "scw kafka [command] --help" for more information about a command.
